content:
It was my pleasure! I'm glad I could help you plan your trip and provide some insider tips for your adventure. You've got a great itinerary ahead of you, and I'm sure you'll have an amazing time exploring the Beartooth Mountains and Cooke City.

Get a good rest, and don't hesitate to reach out if you have any more questions or need further recommendations. Safe travels, and I hope you make some unforgettable memories on your trip!

Sweet dreams, and happy adventuring!
